==Japanese==

===Etymology===
The copula {{m|ja|です|tr=desu}} is thought to be a contracted version of {{m|ja|である|であります|tr=de arimasu}}, from {{compound|ja|だ|alt1=で|tr1=de|ある|alt2=あります|tr2=arimasu|nocat=1}}; however, there are other possibilities, namely {{m|ja|でござる|でございます|tr=de gozaimasu}}, from {{compound|ja|だ|alt1=で|tr1=de|ござる|alt2=ございます|tr2=gozaimasu|nocat=1}}; {{m|ja|でする|tr=de suru}}, from {{compound|ja|だ|alt1=で|tr1=de|する|tr2=suru|nocat=1}}; {{m|ja|でおわす|tr=de owasu}}, from {{compound|ja|だ|alt1=で|tr1=de|おわす|tr2=owasu|nocat=1}}; and {{m|ja|でそうろう|tr=de sourou}}, from {{compound|ja|だ|alt1=で|tr1=de|そうろう|tr2=sourou|nocat=1}}.

